org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.SRM.SW_ResourceCore

Interface SwResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Alarm, DeviceBroker, InterruptResource, MemoryBroker, MemoryPartition, MessageComResource, NotificationResource, SharedDataComResource, SwCommunicationResource, SwConcurrentResource, SwInteractionResource, SwMutualExclusionResource, SwSchedulableResource, SwSynchronizationResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlarmImpl, DeviceBrokerImpl, InterruptResourceImpl, MemoryBrokerImpl, MemoryPartitionImpl, MessageComResourceImpl, NotificationResourceImpl, SharedDataComResourceImpl, SwCommunicationResourceImpl, SwConcurrentResourceImpl, SwInteractionResourceImpl, SwMutualExclusionResourceImpl, SwResourceImpl, SwSchedulableResourceImpl, SwSynchronizationResourceImpl

    public interface SwResource
extends Resource
    A representation of the model object 'Sw Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Identifier Elements
    • State Elements
    • Memory Size Footprint
    • Create Services
    • Delete Services
    • Initialize Services

    See Also:
    SW_ResourceCorePackage.getSwResource()
